            <a id="ntr15-L_202501355EN.000101-E0015" href="#ntc15-L_202501355EN.000101-E0015"
               >(<span class="oj-super">15</span>)</a>  Council Regulation (EC) No 2532/98 of 23 November 1998 concerning the powers of the European Central Bank to impose sanctions (<a href="./../../../legal-content/EN/AUTO/?uri=OJ:L:1998:318:TOC"
